            <thetext>Pressing the &#39;Alt&#39; key or the &#39;AltGr&#39; key lets disappear the focus from the ComboBox.

Using a German keyboard, for example, the &#39;AltGr&#39; key must be used to enter special characters like &#39;@&#39; (AltGr+Q, at symbol) or &#39;€&#39; (AltGr+E, Euro symbol). So these characters cannot be entered.

This is only a problem in the ComboBox. This problem does not exist in the TextField for example.</thetext>
